alluxio.master.file.meta

Class TempInodePathForDescendant

  • java.lang.Object
    • alluxio.master.file.meta.LockedInodePath
      • alluxio.master.file.meta.TempInodePathForDescendant
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    @ThreadSafe
public final class TempInodePathForDescendant
extends LockedInodePath
    This class represents a temporary LockedInodePath. This LockedInodePath will not unlock the inodes on close. This LockedInodePath can set any descendant (does not have to be immediate). This is useful for being able to pass in descendant inodes to methods which require a LockedInodePath, without having to re-traverse the inode tree, and re-acquire locks. This allows methods to operate on descendants associated with an existing LockedInodePath.
